description: Stunning condominium is located in a fully renovated building in a prime South Boston location, offering modern urban living at its best. The spacious open-concept design features a sleek kitchen with custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, and open shelving with LED accent lighting. Beautiful stained wood floors flow throughout, while the primary suite boasts a private tiled bathroom with a luxurious multi-head shower. The custom-tiled main bathroom is equally impressive. Enjoy the convenience of wired-in ceiling speakers and controllers, as well as a private balcony. The home is equipped with efficient forced-air gas heating, central AC, and on-demand tankless hot water. Close to shops, restaurants, Castle Island, parks, and the beach, this is South Boston living at its finest.
